                <h2 data-uuid="7d5d69ce4b53483c9ea2ea9252740605"> Essential Question-Writing</h2>
                <p class="white" data-uuid="9d626c272a804edd934779e5ab8a7228">In this module you’ve
                    learned about the American War for Independence. Now it’s your turn to demonstrate
                    your understanding of the module content by writing an essay.</p>
            </div>
            <h3 data-uuid="54cb4c8560a14bbe97466d0579f24b3e">Why
                were the American Patriots willing to risk their lives for independence?</h3>
            <p data-uuid="cf986c3923234dc9901b4d9e3266ccf1">Write a persuasive essay
                answering this question. Your essay should include details about the
                reasons why American Patriots risked their lives for independence. Be
                sure to cite evidence to support your position and organize your essay into an
                introduction, body, and conclusion.</p>
